                                    will be stored.
The data is used exclusively for the processing of the communication
                                    recording.
The legal basis for the processing of the contact request and its
                                    handling is regularly Art. 6 Para. 1 S.1 lit. b DSGVO.
If further personal data is processed during the sending process,
                                    this is only used to prevent misuse of the contact form and to ensure the security
                                    of our information technology systems.
Your data will be deleted as soon as it is no longer required to
                                    achieve the purpose for which it was collected. For the personal data from the input
                                    mask of the contact form and those sent by e-mail, this is the case when the
                                    respective conversation with the user has ended. The conversation is ended when it
                                    is clear from the circumstances that the matter in question has been conclusively
                                    clarified.
The additional personal data collected during the sending process
                                    will be deleted after a period of seven days at the latest.
