                                    is automatically established upon completion of your order, via which you then
                                    authorise the payment process yourself, if necessary by providing your personal
                                    access data to this provider. In this case, your data is processed exclusively for
                                    the purpose of payment processing, whereby the payment data must regularly be
                                    forwarded by the payment provider to the credit institution specified by you in
                                    order to trigger and authorise the payment transaction.
The processing by plenigo is necessary for the fulfilment of the
                                    contract concluded with you. The legal basis is Art. 6 para. 1 p. 1 lit. b
                                    DSGVO.
For more information, please see plenigo's privacy policy:
https://plenigo.com/datenschutz
